column5: Check this out of you're so inclined. Be sure to watch all the scenes.  Blue Angels
Hey... I can make ya piss your pants and puke in a bag as well ! Just in slow motion compared to that stuff... LOL
I wasn't talking about a ride in your boat Wayne...

man.. look at the face on that dude! i knew i should've went further when i was in air cadets.. was only up to sergeant, flag party commander and 2IC.. ah shucks... could've got my wings when we had flying scholarships.... oh welll.. live and learn...
Good stuff, Dan. And some people have problems hanging a left downtown...go figure.
Man thats amazing footage dan !!!!   that would be awesome to do that,thanks for sharing dan !!!....cheers

Very cool footage!  A friend of mine was on a company trip in the Vegas area and they paid for each employee to go for a ride in high speed jets.  He has video of the whole thing...they did the same kinds of things...people passed out, puked etc.....  He'd do it again in a heartbeat!!  I think it cost $800 per person for about 20 minutes in the air.
that was just great  and that would be fun to try   I love the black outs
Oh man I'd love to try that! I've no doubt that I'd pass out as well and that's probably why I was laughing so hard everytime Steve did.
I really enjoyed it.  Not sure if I need that ride.  Saying I'd do it would be easy.  Doing it is a different story.  Probably not for me.
